title: First-half profit jumps to record at Flying Kangaroo
text:
First-half profit jumps to record at Flying Kangaroo 5:16pm GMT - 01:34 
Australia's Qantas Airways has seen half-year profit jump to a record on cost cuts and hikes in domestic fares - which combined with a share buyback sent its stock bounding higher. Sonia Legg reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
